fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.persistence

Class AbstractPersistenceHandler<P extends PersistenceBackend>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.persistence.AbstractPersistenceHandler<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the PersistenceBackend targeted by this handler.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputHandler, PersistenceHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBlueprintsHandler

    public abstract class AbstractPersistenceHandler<P extends PersistenceBackend>
extends Object
implements PersistenceHandler
    A PersistenceHandler that persists data in a PersistenceBackend, based on received events.
